{
  "texts": [
    "These effects were most prominent when participants had to classify image segments that were generated by different attribution methods (Biessmann & Refiano, 2019; John et al., 2021; Lu et al., 2021; Müller, Thoß, et al., 2024; Selvaraju et al., 2017).",
    "Obviously, this task depends on the attributions as it requires a classification of highly restricted information.",
    "Therefore, it is important to know whether differences between attribution methods were also found in other tasks.",
    "In some cases they were.",
    "One study required participants to report whether the AI had relied on a data artefact (Achtibat et al., 2023)."
  ]
}